---
source: crates/tui/src/ui/mod.rs
expression: body
---

  Prefix actions
    Press C-g first (tmux-style).
    Workspace
      C-g s         New Workspace
      C-g r         Create Worktree (GitHub-only)
      C-g e         Edit Workspace
      C-g d         Delete Workspace
      C-g b         Dashboard
      C-g i         Workspace Info
      C-g w         Switch Workspace (fuzzy)
      C-g }         Next Workspace
      C-g {         Previous Workspace
      C-g `         Toggle Last Workspace
    Git
      C-g g         Git (lazygit)
    Tabs
      C-g c         New Tab
      C-g x         Close Tab
      C-g n         Next Tab
      C-g p         Previous Tab
    Search
      C-g /         Fuzzy File Search
      C-g f         Search in Terminal
    View
      C-g :         Command Palette
      C-g ?         Help
      C-g a         About
      C-g o         Logs
      C-g [         Terminal Scroll Mode
      C-g y         AI Chat
    Focus
      C-g h         Focus Pane Left
      C-g j         Focus Pane Down
      C-g k         Focus Pane Up
      C-g l         Focus Pane Right
    Layout
      C-g <         Shrink Sidebar
      C-g >         Grow Sidebar
      C-g +         Grow Left Split
      C-g -         Shrink Left Split
      Mouse drag    Drag a pane border to resize it
    Clipboard
      C-S-c         Copy Terminal
    Agents
      C-g m         Manage Agents
    Providers
      C-g v         Manage Providers
    App
      C-g q         Quit
    Prefix
      C-g 1..9      Jump to tab N
      C-g C-g       Send the prefix key to the terminal
      Esc           Cancel a pending prefix

  Terminal scroll mode (C-g [)
    j             Scroll down a line
    k             Scroll up a line
    C-d           Page down
    C-u           Page up
    g             Jump to the top
    G             Jump to the bottom
    /             Search the scrollback
    Esc           Exit scroll mode
    q             Exit scroll mode (alt)

  Terminal pane
    (any)         Every key is forwarded to the active tab
    C-S-v         Paste from the clipboard
    Mouse scroll  Scroll the terminal
    Mouse drag    Select text (copies on release)

  Workspace list pane
    j             Select the next workspace
    k             Select the previous workspace
    h             Collapse the group
    l             Expand the group
    Enter         Switch to it / toggle the group

  Agents pane
    j             Select the next agent
    k             Select the previous agent
    Enter         Jump to that workspace and tab
    Click         Jump to that workspace and tab

  Fuzzy file search (C-g /)
    Type          Filter files
    ↓             Select the next result
    ↑             Select the previous result
    Enter         Open in $EDITOR
    C-e           Open in $EDITOR (without closing)
    C-v           Open in the inline editor
    C-o           Open a markdown file in a new tab
    M-m           Open a markdown file in mdr (external)
    Esc           Close

  Command palette (C-g :)
    Type          Filter commands
    ↓             Select the next command
    ↑             Select the previous command
    Enter         Run the selected command
    Esc           Close

  Workspace switcher (C-g w)
    Type          Filter workspaces and tabs
    ↑/↓           Select a row
    C-p           Select the previous row
    C-n           Select the next row
    Enter         Jump to that workspace or tab
    Esc           Close

  Dashboard (C-g b)
    j             Select the next workspace
    k             Select the previous workspace
    Enter         Switch to it and focus the main panel
    Esc           Close

  Logs (C-g o)
    j             Select the next entry
    k             Select the previous entry
    C-d           Page down
    C-u           Page up
    g             Jump to the top
    G             Jump to the bottom
    0-5           Filter by level (0 = all)
    /             Search entries
    r             Toggle auto-refresh (tail)
    Enter         Copy the selected entry
    Esc           Close

  AI Chat overlay (C-g y)
    Enter         Send the message
    Tab           Select the model
    C-o           Settings (server, URL, system prompt)
    C-a           Toggle agent mode (tool use)
    C-l           Clear the conversation
    Esc           Hide (keeps state)

  Kanban board
    h/l/j/k       Navigate columns and cards
    H/L           Move the card left/right
    n / a         New card
    e             Edit the selected card
    d             Delete the card
    D             Dispatch an agent (branch + AI)
    Enter         Toggle card details
    r             Refresh the board
    s             Toggle sort by priority
    /             Search cards
    p             Filter by project
    Esc           Close

  Dispatch agent dialog
    ←/→/Tab       Step 1: cycle the agent / provider
    Type          Step 1: add extra prompt instructions
    Enter         Step 1: continue to the destination
    ←/→/Tab       Step 2: new worktree or current workspace
    Enter         Step 2: dispatch
    Esc           Back a step, or cancel

  Move dispatched card (after confirming delete)
    j/k           Select the target kanban column
    Enter         Move the card and delete the workspace
    Esc           Cancel

  Manage agents (C-g m)
    j/k           Navigate the agent list
    n             New agent (step 1: name + provider)
    e / Enter     Edit the selected agent
    d             Delete the selected agent
    p             Sync the agent to the repo
    i             Import agents from the repo
    Esc           Close

  Agent role editor (step 2)
    C-s           Save the agent and close
    Esc           Back to step 1 without saving

  Import agents overlay
    j/k           Navigate the discovered agents
    Space         Toggle the selection
    a             Toggle select-all
    Enter         Import the selected agents
    Esc           Cancel

  Manage providers (C-g v)
    j/k           Navigate the provider list
    n             New provider
    e / Enter     Edit the selected provider
    d             Delete the selected provider
    Esc           Close

  Inline editor
    C-s           Save
    Esc           Close

  Code Review (requires gh CLI, locked mode)
    j/k           Navigate files / scroll the diff
    Enter         View the file diff
    h/l           Switch between the file list and the diff
    n/p           Next / previous file (in the diff view)
    g/G           Top / bottom of the diff
    C-d           Page down in the diff
    C-u           Page up in the diff
    c             Add or edit a comment on the line
    d             Delete the comment on the line
    [ / ]         Resize the file list / diff split
    s             Open the submit-review dialog
    r             Refresh the PR data
    q             Close the review (discards state)
    Tab           Cycle the verdict (in submit)
    C-S-d         Discard the draft (in submit)
